# Pytest leakage: main.py mkdirs settings.renders_dir on app boot, and
# TestClient triggers that from tests/ as cwd even when individual tests
# monkeypatch renders_dir. Safe to commit a stray tests/renders/ sentinel
# would not be — just ignore it.
tests/renders/

